Soul singer Timi Dakolo has shared some of the things that make him feel rich. Dakolo, a father of three, shared with fans a screenshot of Whatsapp chat he had with his first offspring, Alexander. Dakolo said such conversation with his son makes him feel rich.   Tiwa Savage: The kind of guy I’m looking for     Kizz Daniel, Davido excite fans with joint EP announcement     How to identify fake cosmetic surgeons, by Mary Njoku   The Whatsapp chat reads: Alex wrote: “Good morning, Daddy. I love you. It’s Alex. I love you. Be safe. I love you.” “I love you too Alexander. Going to the clinic now,” Dakolo replied. Alex added: “Be safe, I love you. Miss you so much. Daddy pls be safe. Promise me you will be ok. Pls be safe daddy. I love you so much. Just know I am here for you.” Captioning the post, the “Everything (Amen)” hit singer wrote: “The things that make me feel Rich. Chairman @alexanderdakolo. The son of my youth.”